<h4 id="policy-process-and-procedure">policy, process and procedure</h4>
<ol>
  <li>policy: a course or principle of action adopted or proposed by an organisation or individual.
    <ul>
      <li>we see policy as being the rules and expectations around a particular thing.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>process: a series of actions or steps taken in order to achieve a particular end.</li>
  <li>procedure: an established or official way of doing something.
    <ul>
      <li>the detailed instructions of steps</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ol>

<h4 id="word">Word</h4>
